decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color:=
 #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> the FDIC=E2=
=80=99s announcement</a>, though =E2=80=9CThis is an estimate and the final=
 cost will be determined when the FDIC terminates the receivership.=E2=80=
=9D</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">
<em>Equity:</em> JPMorgan is getting about $186 billion of assets for about=
 $182.6 billion ($122 billion of assumed liabilities, plus $10.6 billion in=
